  "instructions": [
    "heat ghee in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "add galangal and saut\u00175 till fragrant, about 2 minutes.",
    "add allspice, curry powder, brown sugar, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "reduce heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.",
    "stir in coconut milk, scotch bonnet peppers, and lime juice.",
    "serve in a Korean brass bowl topped with coconut cream and garnished with green onions.",
    "allow coconut cream to set and crisp up in refrigerator for at least 30 minutes."
